quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  11,50,"Ndipo kwa mtundu wa Aad, tidatumiza m’bale wawo Hud. Iye adati: “Oh anthu anga! Pembedzani Mulungu. Inu mulibe mulungu wina kupatula Iye yekha. Ndithudi inu simuchita china chili chonse koma kupeka bodza basi.”"
  11,51,“oh anthu anga! Ine sindikukupemphani malipiro pazimenezi. Malipiro anga sali ndi wina koma ali ndi Iye amene adandilenga. Kodi simutha kumva zimenezi?”
  11,52,“oh Anthu anga! Mpempheni Ambuye wanu chikhululukiro ndipo lapani kwa Iye chifukwa Iye adzakutumizirani mvula yambiri ndipo adzakuonjezerani mphamvu pamwamba pa mphamvu zanu. Kotero musatembenuke kukhala anthu oipa.”
  11,53,"Iwo adati, “oh iwe Hud! Iwe siunatibweretsere umboni wokwana. Ndipo ife sitidzasiya kupembedza milungu yathu chifukwa cha mawu ako! Ndipo ife sitikukhulupirira iwe ayi.”"
  11,54,"“Zimene tilikunena ndizakuti ina ya milungu yathu yakupatsa iwe tsoka.” Iye adati: “Ndithudi Mulungu ndiye mboni yanga ndipo nanunso chitirani umboni kuti ine ndatalikirana nazo zimene mukamapembedza mulikuonjezera.”"
  11,55,“Motero nonsenu konzani chiwembu chanu pa ine ndipo musandichedwetse.”
  11,56,"“Ine ndaika chikhulupiliro changa mwa Mulungu, Ambuye wanga ndiponso Ambuye wanu. Palibe chinthu cha moyo pa dziko lapansi chimene tsogolo lake sililamulidwa ndi Iye. Ndithudi Ambuye wanga ndi amene ali pa njira yoyenera.”"
  11,57,"“Ndipo ngati mutembenuka, ine ndakuuzani Uthenga umene ndatumizidwa kwa inu. Ambuye wanga adzaika, m’malo mwanu, anthu ena ndipo inu simungamuchite chinthu choipa chilichonse. Ndithudi Ambuye wanga ndi Msungi wa zinthu zonse.”"
  11,58,"Ndipo pamene chiweruzo chathu chidadza, Ife tidamupulumutsa Hud, kudzera mu Chisomo chathu, pamodzi ndi amene adakhulupirira ndi iye. Ife tidawapulumutsa ku chilango chokhwima"
  11,59,"Amenewa anali anthu a Aad. Iwo adakana Mawu a Ambuye wawo, ndipo adanyoza Atumwi ake ndipo anatsata malamulo a atsogoleri awo a nkhanza ndi okana chilungamo"
  11,60,"Ndipo iwo adatsatiridwa ndi temberero m’dziko lino ndipo adzakhala otembereredwa pa tsiku la chiweruzo. Mosakaika, ndithudi, anthu a Ad adamukana Ambuye wawo. Motero tinathana nawo Ad, anthu a Hud"